p: Out of the nine DENV-3 samples, three were identified as genotype I ( Fig 4). These grouped together and clustered with strains collected over the past decade from Southeast Asian countries (Indonesia, Singapore, Malaysia) and Australia ( Fig 4, label a). The six remaining DENV-3 strains belonged to the genotype III, although they were derived from multiple lineages circulating over the last decade in Southeast Asian countries, including Laos, Vietnam, Malaysia and Thailand ( Fig 4, labels b and c).
